  <FFF.Drone.AllowedAreaDesc>設置許可活動區域，新部屬以及部屬中的無人機將自動同步平台的活動區設置。</FFF.Drone.AllowedAreaDesc>

  <!-- EN: control platform unavailable -->
  <FFF.Drone.NoControlPlatform>主控平台不可用</FFF.Drone.NoControlPlatform>
  <!-- EN: No control -->
  <FFF.Drone.NoController>沒有主控</FFF.Drone.NoController>
  <!-- EN: platform not controlled -->
  <FFF.Drone.ControllerNotInControl>主控不受控制</FFF.Drone.ControllerNotInControl>
  <!-- EN: platform not drafted -->
  <FFF.Drone.ControllerNotDrafted>主控未受徵招</FFF.Drone.ControllerNotDrafted>
  <!-- EN: platform not exist in the map -->
  <FFF.Drone.ControllerNotInMap>主控不存在於地圖內</FFF.Drone.ControllerNotInMap>

  <!-- EN: Will detonate explosives payloads after collision -->
  <FFF.ExplosiveOnDead>機體在碰撞後會引爆攜帶的爆炸物</FFF.ExplosiveOnDead>

  <!-- EN: Prioritize filling {0}x{1} -->
  <FFF.FillMechPlatform>優先填充{0}x{1}</FFF.FillMechPlatform>

  <!-- EN: Return to platform -->
  <FFF.Drone.Return>返回部署平台</FFF.Drone.Return>
  <!-- EN: Commands drone return to the deployment platform and shut down, which will restore the consumed resources. -->
  <FFF.Drone.ReturnDesc>命令該無人機返回部署平台並關機，這將恢復部署無人機時的資源消耗。</FFF.Drone.ReturnDesc>

  <!-- EN: The deployment platform for {0} is unavailable -->
  <FFF.Drone.NoPlatform>{0}的部署平台不可用</FFF.Drone.NoPlatform>

  <!-- EN: Deploy {0} -->
  <FFF.DeployDrone>部署 {0}</FFF.DeployDrone>
  <!-- EN: Consume stored {0} to deploy up to {1} {2} drones. If the platform is destroyed, all {3} controlled by it will shut down. {4} operates on internal batteries and automatically returns to the platform when the battery is low. -->
  <FFF.DeployDroneDesc>命令平台消耗儲存的{0}來部署最多{1}架的{2}無人機。如果部署平台被破壞，所有受其控制的{3}都會關停。{4}使用內置電池運作，並在電量不足時自動返回平台來回收部署時的消耗。</FFF.DeployDroneDesc>

  <!-- EN: Auto Deploy -->
  <FFF.AutoDeploy>自動部署</FFF.AutoDeploy>
  <!-- EN: Command this platform to automatically deploy and undeploy drones at a stable interval. -->
  <FFF.AutoDeployDesc>命令此平台以穩定的間隔週期自動部署與部署無人機。</FFF.AutoDeployDesc>
  <!-- EN: Auto Deploy Enable -->
  <FFF.AutoDeployEnabled>自動部署激活</FFF.AutoDeployEnabled>
  <!-- EN: Deployment interval: {0} -->
  <FFF.WillDeployAt>部署間隔: {0}</FFF.WillDeployAt>

  <!-- EN: Retract all {0} -->
  <FFF.RetractDrones>收回所有 {0}</FFF.RetractDrones>
  <!-- EN: Command all {0} controlled by this platform to withdraw, which will replenish the {1} consumption. -->
  <FFF.RetractDronesDesc>命令所有由此平台所控制的{0}撤回部署平台，這將補充平台部署無人機時的{1}消耗。</FFF.RetractDronesDesc>

